LUCALI is by far the BEST pizza in the country. We are foodies , as well as culinary chefs, who have a love and an appreciation for fresh, simple, authentic food, Lucali is all of the above. The pie is a perfectly made , the cheeses and the sauce which are made fresh every day make this pizza expierence exquisite., not to mention the service was fantastic! A must try at least once in your life time, no doubt you will be back for more....
